\end{equation}

\end_inset


\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

It is worth noting that as 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu\rightarrow\infty$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $Var[x]\rightarrow1.0$
